            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Okay, then. Let's see... Where did I put it...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I thought I put that large flask in here somewhere... But I can't find it anywhere..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "This is the book I bought a few weeks ago... And this is the wrapper from those sweets..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Maybe I put it further inside... What's back here...? Uwah! These ingredients are all dried up!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I'll make sure to use them for some synthesis soon... Hm? What's that?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0xf,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Clothes...? Why are there clothes in my container?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x50,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "If Monika found out about this... Oh, I'd be in big trouble..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x52,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I guess it's just as well I found them myself first. I'll just put them away in my drawers... Huh?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "These aren't my clothes at all. They're really old... Wait a minute!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0xf,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I think these belonged to Grandma! This is a real find!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Let's check the size... Perfect! Which means she must have worn these when she was my age..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Wow, Grandma's clothes... Hehe... What a find!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "...I feel like this is just meant to be. I should try them on... Woah!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "They're all moth-eaten! I can't wear these... Oh, but of course!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Now's the perfect time to use alchemy! Surely alchemy can be used to fix clothes!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x45,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Okay, then! It's time to officially launch the \"Fix Grandma's Clothes Project\"!"
        }
    ]
}